org.apache.juneau.transforms

Class XMLGregorianCalendarSwap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.transform.PojoSwap<T,String>
      • org.apache.juneau.transform.StringSwap<XMLGregorianCalendar>
        • org.apache.juneau.transforms.XMLGregorianCalendarSwap

  • public class XMLGregorianCalendarSwap
extends StringSwap<XMLGregorianCalendar>
    Transforms XMLGregorianCalendars to ISO8601 date-time Strings.

    Objects are converted to strings using XMLGregorianCalendar.toXMLFormat().

    Strings are converted to objects using DatatypeFactory.newXMLGregorianCalendar(String).
